<taxonomicName id="517C082008FCB1EE31E40E201659F2D1" authority="(Poir.) Rich." class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Spiranthes" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="null" pageNumber="607" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="aestivalis">
<pageBreakToken id="964EDFAB21CD879C811105A211A5A6DB" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">Spiranthes</pageBreakToken>
<normalizedToken id="99E82498A27501C90DAB821B92356DCC" originalValue="aestivális" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">aestivalis</normalizedToken>
(Poir.) Rich.
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="275BE02FBC505AB89A390FFA5773DAAE" pageId="null" pageNumber="607" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="1CC14708240165E4FF6C1057E1875621" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">Sommer-Wendelorchis</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="0A73F5A157C98F954B57ECC13E90AF06" pageId="null" pageNumber="607" type="description">
<paragraph id="F0A48A5A4301E442AF71B4D6D3A1E40E" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">
<emphasis id="F602732A9254E1F8D8B5C029B6D79975" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">
Keine 
<normalizedToken id="DD566FC009BF2A3BAC6EFD2CC134068E" originalValue="seitenständige" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">seitenstaendige</normalizedToken>
Grundblattrosette. Untere 
<normalizedToken id="1345FAE39290C7086B622C35F80346E2" originalValue="Stengelblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">Stengelblaetter</normalizedToken>
schmal lanzettlich, bis 10 cm lang, 8-15mal so lang wie breit
</emphasis>
, obere 
<normalizedToken id="6898884184DE99F8EC8663C94EECE2FA" originalValue="Stengelblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">Stengelblaetter</normalizedToken>
schuppenartig (wie bei 
<taxonomicName id="F0C045FCE531B8ABF769E1BE0D16152D" authority="Nr." authorityName="Nr." class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Spiranthes" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="null" pageNumber="607" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="spiralis">
<emphasis id="0773DBAEEC5CEDF3C5F35AF250DDC6F1" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">S. spiralis</emphasis>
, Nr.
</taxonomicName>
1). 
<normalizedToken id="339C72B534B3536C5C3AB1944715839C" originalValue="Blütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">Bluetenstand</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="78F52DF1552EFB7BB471384FABCDA588" originalValue="Blüten" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">Blueten</normalizedToken>
wie bei 
<taxonomicName id="AD07194F881AEFDBB44D6EC51417D309" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Spiranthes" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="null" pageNumber="607" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="spiralis">
<emphasis id="8F6A83CD38685D388053722C514878B5" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">S. spiralis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, jedoch lockerer mit 
<normalizedToken id="B87EA8D0F5C6A07A08EF330CF7A74ED4" originalValue="Drüsen" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">Druesen</normalizedToken>
besetzt und die 
<emphasis id="ECFD87F45CFE0EBD9C4EDF55B392200A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">
<normalizedToken id="0810CCB4F760BD29DF4BD661A17DF797" originalValue="Perigonblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">Perigonblaetter</normalizedToken>
4-6 mm lang. -
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="78D8B18EF1194212CEFCEA954E6395A9" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4390DC83CBD5651A53A3AAAB5F8288A8" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">
<emphasis id="91B04D1ADFFDF8497D11EAE1217E9282" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1FC29642946CA043B7C1CC98683A114F" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">
<emphasis id="42CBC8B9B1852617293F111C3A1AFAD5" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">
<pageBreakToken id="D278A4D619E60959E9959A9BBA6B9ACD" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">Standort</pageBreakToken>
.
</emphasis>
Kollin und montan. Nasse, humose 
<normalizedToken id="0076E4DD80346D6EFED89C8DA820ABF1" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">Boeden</normalizedToken>
mit biogenen Kalkausscheidungen (Tuff), Flachmoore, besonders im 
<emphasis id="08A0B33B66BC294FD710230D8F2E9423" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">Schoenetum</emphasis>
auct. (Kopfbinsenwiesen).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B0EEAA53D2D9B51F7C1846E97C378447" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">
<emphasis id="C34C0DADA36CED57E4299A6B9B42FC9C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="06C646C166C62778912F190FABB0BEAA" originalValue="Europäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">Europaeische</normalizedToken>
Pflanze:
</emphasis>
Wie 
<taxonomicName id="C0AD11ACE1D9E06628222AC59CC08617" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Spiranthes" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="null" pageNumber="607" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="spiralis">
<emphasis id="71B13079379960F3C8F7195EF738F9EB" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">S. spiralis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 1), jedoch 
<normalizedToken id="55FCEDE7C4C5113FB6F3AD47F2192824" originalValue="nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
nur bis Kanalinseln, 
<normalizedToken id="2AD432B951A2D7DD505F84B7316885A4" originalValue="Süddeutschland" pageId="null" pageNumber="607">Sueddeutschland</normalizedToken>
und Tschechoslowakei. - Im Gebiet zerstreut, ziemlich selten.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</treatment>
